On Saturday the 28th of April,<a href="http://arrg.co.uk/">Auld Reekie Roller Girls</a> host the much anticipated final of their first Home Season in style with a double header.First up is a bout between Arrg's <a href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Cherry-Bombers/274799135908869">Cherry Bombers</a> and <a href="http://glasgowrollerderby.com/">Glasgow Roller Derby's</a> Hells Belles.The main event is to decide which Home Team will be crowned champions and will see the <a href="http://www.facebook.com/theskatefastclub">Skatefast Club</a> go up against the <a href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Leithal-Weapons/209794282441077">Leithal Weapons</a> in what should be a really hard fought bout. 
